(137, 'contempo-notifier-cache', '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>\n									<notifier>\n										<latest>2.7.7</latest>\n										<changelog>\n											<![CDATA[\n												<h5><strong>Version 2.7.7 - June 10th, 2015</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes under the hood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7.6 - December 22nd, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Github icon added to social icons list</li>\r\n<li>Minor CSS fixes for Firefox</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7.5 - December&nbsp;17th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Composition images Landspace / Portait options updated for custom post types as Full width / Half width</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7.4 - November&nbsp;3rd, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Facebook like button fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7.3 - October&nbsp;30th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Left aligned menu sub item fix</li>\r\n<li>Google Fonts list update</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7.2 - September 12th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Google Map plugin update</li>\r\n<li>Composition section rich text editor fix</li>\r\n<li>Scrollbar styling option fix</li>\r\n<li>IMDB social icon added</li>\r\n<li>Sharing buttons fix : Facebook share button replaced with native JS,Vkontakte replaced with image due to JS issues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7.1 - September&nbsp;2nd, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thumbnail attribute fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.7 - July 14th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&ldquo;Social Icons&rdquo; and &ldquo;Search Box&rdquo; can be shown in header on Full Width Layout (Reframe &gt; Main Layout &gt; Main Layout as Full Width)</li>\r\n<li>Disable Floating Menu / Project Info Sidebar feature fix.</li>\r\n<li>Nicescroll Plugin (Browser scrollbar styling) fix. For performance reasons, native CSS3 / Webkit browser scrollbar styling has been integrated. Nicescroll Plugin will only be activated on Non-Webkit (Firefox and IE) browsers.</li>\r\n<li>Left menu Ajax loading issues fix.</li>\r\n<li>Composition text field fix : link and source code buttons added</li>\r\n<li>Etsy icon added to the social icon set</li>\r\n<li>Minor fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.6.3 - June 27th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes under the hood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.6.2 - June 5th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Image caption alignment fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes under the hood</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.6.1 - June 5th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Text editor image align center fix</li>\r\n<li>Browser history fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.6 - May&nbsp;23rd, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="\\">History.js Plugin added to fix browser history issues</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="\\">Nicescroll Plugin updated</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.5.9 - April 19th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Wordpress V3.9 compatibility fix : short code button replaced</li>\r\n<li>Left menu styling fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.5.8 - April 10th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Swipebox Lightbox Plugin updated. Mobile touch screen issues fixed</li>\r\n<li>New Galleria options : Centreal &gt; Gallery &gt; Disable Mobile Double Tap&nbsp;and Disable Fullscreen Feature</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.5.7 - March 27th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>DB setup fix for new installation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.5.6 - March 23rd, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Logo width fix for responsive layout</li>\r\n<li>Thumbnail overlay alignment fixed for Internet Explorer</li>\r\n<li>Contact form error message colour set to global link colour setting</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.5.5 - March 14th, 2014</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Title function fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.5.4 - March 13th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New options for slider ; Reframe &gt; Slider &gt; Pause on Mouseover, Hide&nbsp;Slider Navigation Arrows</li>\r\n<li>Ajax navigation fix for mobile</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.5.3 - February 20th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mobile and tablet view issues fixed for &ldquo;Remove header&rdquo; option</li>\r\n<li>Project info alignment fix</li>\r\n<li>B&amp;W reinitialization fix for ajax navigation</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.5.2 - February 20th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Custom Post Type page fix for iPhone</li>\r\n<li>Floating sidebar content width fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug and CSS fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.5.1 - February 18th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Intro slider main menu issue fix</li>\r\n<li>B&amp;W effect re-initialization fix for ajax navigation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.5 - February 18th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Custom Post Overview Page Isotope plugin fix. Page initialization and&nbsp;CSS effects are more stable and fixed for responsive layout.</li>\r\n<li>Black &amp; White mouseover effect for custom post type page thumbnails.&nbsp;Reframe &gt; Main Layout &gt; Black &amp; White Mouseover Effect for Thumbnails</li>\r\n<li>Floating Left Menu and Project Sidebar fixed.</li>\r\n<li>Display Main Text Content option is added for Custom Post Type and&nbsp;Blog template. It allows to display text editor content below or above&nbsp;the main page content.</li>\r\n<li>Swipebox integration for WP galleries</li>\r\n<li>Tag page title fix</li>\r\n<li>Lightbox caption quotes fix</li>\r\n<li>Lightbox transparency fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.4.1 - February 6th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Contact form &ldquo;From&rdquo; field fix</li>\r\n<li>Gallery short code fix</li>\r\n<li>Post Sharing button image URL fix</li>\r\n<li>Custom Post Type Category ordering fix</li>\r\n<li>Search function fix</li>\r\n<li>Single project floating sidebar fix ; it must be disabled if Related&nbsp;Posts activated.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.4.01 - January 30th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.4 - January 29th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>NEW FEATURE : Fancybox support has been removed due to script&nbsp;conflicts and outdated features. Instead, fullscreen, responsive and&nbsp;mobile / touchscreen activated Swipebox Lighbox Plugin is integrated.&nbsp;Settings can be changed from Reframe &gt; Lightbox section and&nbsp;instructions can be seen at the theme documentation, Lightbox section.</li>\r\n<li>NEW FEATURE : Video embed code can be used instead of featured image&nbsp;on custom post type overview page.</li>\r\n<li>NEW FEATURE : Related Posts can be displayed on single post pages.&nbsp;Workality &gt; Custom Post Type &gt; Step 1 Options : Display Related&nbsp;Posts,Title, Thumbnail Type, Related Post Limit, Show Posts from Same&nbsp;Category, Random Posts.</li>\r\n<li>JQuery, Modernizr plugins are updated to the latest versions.</li>\r\n<li>Remove/Disable Header feature is added to framework - Reframe &gt; Main&nbsp;Layout &gt; Remove Header. It allows to remove header (logo, social icons,&nbsp;top menu) and align the left menu/logo and page content at the top.</li>\r\n<li>Disable Navigation Arrows, Disable Navigation Arrow Text options are&nbsp;added to Reframe &gt; Custom Posts</li>\r\n<li>Top and bottom sharing buttons can be disabled separately for single&nbsp;custom post pages.</li>\r\n<li>RSS feed fix. Also post thumbnails included into RSS feed (Thanks to&nbsp;Victor Dallen)</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.3.11 - January 15th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Single Custom Post Page project navigation thumbnail fixed.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.3.1 - January 13th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Blog featured image fix</li>\r\n<li>Sub Category HTML title fix (Parent Category / Sub Category | Site&nbsp;Name)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.3 - January 11th, 2014</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Category ordering section is added to the framework. Reframe &gt;&nbsp;Category Ordering</li>\r\n<li>Performance upgrade and error check for all theme files. Custom Post&nbsp;Page and Single Post Page performance is increased</li>\r\n<li>Archive, Category, Tag, Search page issues are fixed in terms of&nbsp;content, HTML title and navigation</li>\r\n<li>Slider caption issue fix. Caption Alignment / Text color and Caption</li>\r\n<li>Text Alignment options are added into Workality &gt; Sliders section.</li>\r\n<li>Browser Back/Forward button functioning is fixed for mobile devices</li>\r\n<li>Linkedin post sharing button was added : Workality &gt; Posts Sharing &gt;&nbsp;Linkedin</li>\r\n<li>Reframe &gt; Gallery &gt; Disable Image Preload. Useful when high number of&nbsp;images are used for gallery</li>\r\n<li>Admin panel media Library search feature fix</li>\r\n<li>Back to top button is activated for Smart Phones and Tablets</li>\r\n<li>Responsive styling is added for Wordpress Native Video Player</li>\r\n<li>Custom Post Overview page fixed for Tablet</li>\r\n<li>Empty categories are set not to display</li>\r\n<li>Author page fix</li>\r\n<li>Flexslider updated to the latest version and cross browser&nbsp;compatibility fixed. Additional options are added into theme framework&nbsp;: Reframe &gt; Slider &gt; &ldquo;Icon Colors&rdquo;, &ldquo;Enable&nbsp;Caption Auto-Hide&rdquo;</li>\r\n<li>Pagination limit fix for category/tag pages</li>\r\n<li>Category page title fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.2.2 - December 3rd, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Category / Taxonomy page HTML title fix</li>\r\n<li>Thumbnail overlapping issue fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.2.1 - December 3rd, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Blog archive/category pagination limit fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.2 - November 29th, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Blog featured content alignment can be changed as top or below the&nbsp;post title on the single post page. Reframe &gt; Blog Layout &gt; Blog&nbsp;featured content alignment</li>\r\n<li>Fancybox support is added to the Composition section images. Images&nbsp;can be activated for Fancybox if the Fancybox plugin is installed :&nbsp;http://wordpress.org/plugins/fancybox-for-wordpress/</li>\r\n<li>Make URL functions is updated. Http:// and www will be automatically&nbsp;trimmed from the project custom fields URLs.</li>\r\n<li>Fixed thumbnail alignment is fixed for longer titles and tablet&nbsp;viewport.</li>\r\n<li>SEO fix for single posts</li>\r\n<li>\\"View\\" button won\\''t be displayed if \\"More\\" tag is used for the&nbsp;Standard Format Post in order to prevent duplicate link.</li>\r\n<li>Editor Styles</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.1.4 - November 7th, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Intro Slider link issue has been fixed. If the current slide\\''s URL&nbsp;value is blank, it won\\''t be clickable.</li>\r\n<li>Left Menu ajax navigation issues have been fixed.</li>\r\n<li>Left Menu styling issue has been fixed.</li>\r\n<li>Selected menu item styling for the Top Menu has been fixed. Parent&nbsp;menu will have the \\"selected\\" styling if its submenu item is selected.</li>\r\n<li>Reframe &gt; Posts Slider &gt; Disable Autoplay option has been added.</li>\r\n<li>Custom Post Type category navigation menu has been fixed.</li>\r\n<li>Widget areas have been fixed.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.1.3 - October 31st, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fullpage Slider main logo size fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.1.2 - October 29th, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Font Awesome Library is downgraded to V3.2.1 to avoid conflicts</li>\r\n<li>Size option for icon shortcodes</li>\r\n<li>Google Fonts fix for header/body font settings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.1.1 - October 28th, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Font Awesome library is updated (V4.0.1)</li>\r\n<li>Intro slider caption issues fixed</li>\r\n<li>Back to top button is added. It can be disabled through Reframe &gt;&nbsp;Main Layout &gt; Disable Back to Top Button</li>\r\n<li>Date functions are fixed for localization support</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Version 2.1 - October 24th, 2013</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Composition and Slider section uploaders are replaced with Wordpress&nbsp;Media Uploader. <strong>Multiple image</strong> upload is allowed.</li>\r\n<li>New option ; <strong>Workality &gt; Gallery &gt; Center-Aligned Thumbnails</strong>. It&nbsp;allows to center gallery thumbnails below the gallery.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.0.1 - October 21st, 2013</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Intro slider panel fix</li>\r\n<li>Intro slider initialization fix \\"fade in\\" effect</li>\r\n<li>Browser window frame color fix</li>\r\n<li>Left menu ajax category/post navigation fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 2.0 - October 17th, 2013</strong></h5>\r\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT :</strong> If you\\''ll upgrade your theme from a previous version, please backup your intro slider content since Intro Slider has been completely renewed and content must be created through Pages section. Furthermore, @fontface feature has been added to the Reframe and you\\''re supposed to navigate Reframe &gt; Fonts section to set up your font preferences once you upgraded your theme. Source Code Pro (from Google Fonts) font is used at live theme demo.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>NEW FEATURE :</strong> Completely renewed Intro Slider ; Slider is replaced&nbsp;with Supersized plugin.</li>\r\n<li>+ Videos (youtube, vimeo) can be used in slides as well as images.</li>\r\n<li>+ Captions can be used with slides.</li>\r\n<li>+ Slides can be generated through intro slider panel at Pages section&nbsp;instead of theme framework. By this means, multiple intro slider pages&nbsp;can be created with their own slider content.</li>\r\n<li><strong>NEW FEATURE :</strong> <a href="https://northeme.com/wp-admin/\\">@fontface</a> support. Google Fonts, <a href="https://northeme.com/wp-admin/\\">@fontface</a> and HTML&nbsp;font options can be set from Reframe &gt; Fonts.</li>\r\n<li>Reframe &gt; Custom Posts &gt; Display Date, Display Category options are&nbsp;added. BG color, text color and transparent BG options can be set for&nbsp;the corresponding custom posts (for Inside / Overlay option)</li>\r\n<li>Browser Frame is completely renewed for height issues. Bottom border&nbsp;and HTML structure are fixed to prevent bottom spacing.</li>\r\n<li>External link \\"Open in new window / Open in Same window\\" option is&nbsp;added for Blog and Custom Posts.</li>\r\n<li>SEO issues are fixed for custom post types.</li>\r\n<li>Permalink updating issue is fixed.</li>\r\n<li>New options at theme framework :</li>\r\n<li>+ Reframe &gt; Fonts &gt; Font Types (<a href="https://northeme.com/wp-admin/\\">@fontface</a>, Google Fonts, HTML Fonts)</li>\r\n<li>+ Reframe &gt; Main Layout &gt; Disable scrollbar styling (allows to use&nbsp;default scrollbar)</li>\r\n<li>+ Reframe &gt; Intro Slider. Slider content removed since content can be&nbsp;created at Pages section. New options : Caption styling, enable caption&nbsp;text shadow, slider transition type, navigation arrow hide/show,&nbsp;slideshow play/pause button hide/show, navigation arrow color, random&nbsp;slides, disable autoplay.</li>\r\n<li>+ Reframe &gt; Social Icons &gt; Hide social icons at the bottom of left menu</li>\r\n<li>Category menu fixed for mobile view</li>\r\n<li>Several minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 1.5.7 - September 4th, 2013</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Main menu fix ; Blog categories navigation and accordion menu fix</li>\r\n<li>Category show/hide option fix for single post types</li>\r\n<li>Localization file updated</li>\r\n<li>Updated files : default.mo, default.po, functions.php, /js/master.js, single-works-content.php</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 1.5.6 - August 19, 2013</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>All custom post types are included into the search results</li>\r\n<li>Password protected form input fix</li>\r\n<li>Custom post types \\"Show All\\" link fix</li>\r\n<li>Social icons : Vimeo logo fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>Version 1.5.5 - August 06, 2013</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Deprecated functions were replaced and minor issues were fixed for&nbsp;Wordpress 3.6</li>\r\n<li>Homepage pagination \\"Load More\\" button was fixed</li>\r\n<li>Menu default / rollover states were fixed</li>\r\n<li>Galleria fullscreen button and maximum image scale issues were fixed.</li>\r\n<li>Social icons fixed for Android devices</li>\r\n<li>Minor fixes ; PHP mb_strupper extension was fixed for compatibility&nbsp;issues</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5.4 - August 05, 2013 </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Main menu styling option fix (Reframe &gt; Header Settings &gt; Main Menu Styling)</li>\r\n<li>Main menu hover/active color setting fix (Reframe &gt; Styling Options &gt; Color Presets)</li>\r\n<li>Category menu and minor fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5.32 - August 01, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Main menu issue fixed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5.31 - July 31, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minor javascript fixes for custom post pages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5.3 - July 30, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mobile/Table menu icon was replaced for retina display</li>\r\n<li>Header/Footer social icons switch fixed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5.2 - July 30, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Left menu ajax post navigation fix</li>\r\n<li>Minor script fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5.1 - July 29, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minor script fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.5 - July 29, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span data-mce-mark="\\">Retina Display Support (It can be disabled via Workality &gt; Advanced)</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-mce-mark="\\">Footer social icon set is replaced with Socialico @fontface set for&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-mark="\\">Retina support. 32 different social icon is ready to use.</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-mce-mark="\\">Footer social icon interface (Reframe &gt; Social Icons) is completely&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-mark="\\">improved.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-mce-mark="\\">Password protected pages support is improved : Default page template, Full width template, Custom post template&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-mce-mark="\\">Post navigation arrows fix for single blog pages.</span></li>\r\n<li><span data-mce-mark="\\">Main menu fix for tablet viewport.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li>UPDATE INSTRUCTIONS&nbsp;: In order to use retina support and medium (regular) thumbnail&nbsp;size of custom post types, installing Regenerate Thumbnail plugin is required to generate corresponding thumbnails. Once it\\''s installed, the thumbnails can be re-generated via&nbsp;Tools &gt; Reg Thumbnails option. <a href="https://northeme.com/wp-admin/\\">http://wordpress.org/plugins/regenerate-thumbnails/ </a>If you don\\''t want to use retina feature, you\\''re able to deactivate it via Reframe &gt; Advanced &gt; Disable Retina Support. As for footer social icons, you\\''re supposed to re-add your social&nbsp;links once the theme is updated from a previous version.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.4 - July 10, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Author page is fixed and rearranged</li>\r\n<li>Search page is fixed</li>\r\n<li>Single blog page top margin issue fixed</li>\r\n<li>Minor widget styling fix</li>\r\n<li>Changed files :&nbsp;author.php, loop-item.php, loop-search.php, search.php, single-blog-content.php, style.css, template-blog-content.php</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.9 - July 10, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pagination fix for custom post types and blog</li>\r\n<li>New option ; Blog Layout &gt; Pagination Limit. Settings &gt; Reading &gt;</li>\r\n<li>\\"Blog pages show at most\\" option will be ignored.</li>\r\n<li>Single custom post type page mobile viewport fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.8 - July 8, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Slider fix ; duration and animation type. New parameter added ; Animation speed.</li>\r\n<li>New option for Intro slider ; Hide navigation arrows</li>\r\n<li>Pagination fix for blog and custom post types</li>\r\n<li>Single custom post type page fix for mobile</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.7 - June 24, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Custom post name sanitize function fix</li>\r\n<li>Additional slash fix for single custom post pages</li>\r\n<li>New option for Custom Posts : <strong>Reframe &gt; Custom Posts &gt; Hide&nbsp;categories on single custom post page</strong></li>\r\n<li>Fix for multiple google map instances</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.6 - June 17, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>If external URL is set # (hashtag), thumbnails will be unclickable.</li>\r\n<li>Standard Post Format is updated for right info alignment. Title, category, author will be shown in right column and post content in left column.</li>\r\n<li>Single custom post navigation arrows update the active single post in main menu (if applicable).</li>\r\n<li>Minor theme framework fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.5 - June 13, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Single blog posts fix : Hide \\"Share :\\" text if any sharing button wasn\\''t turned on and display comments option is fixed.</li>\r\n<li>Logo size is fixed for cross browser compatibility.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.4 - June 12, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New Option : Reframe &gt; Main Layout &gt;&nbsp;Custom Post Single Page Info/Navigation Placement. This option allows you to set single custom post \\"info/navigation sidebar\\" alignment as <strong>right</strong> or <strong>top</strong>.</li>\r\n<li>Minor theme framework fix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.3 - June 10, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New \\"Show in sidebar\\" option for Display Project Content&nbsp;in single custom posts.</li>\r\n<li>Main logo maximum width value fix</li>\r\n<li>Browser back button fix for ajax</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3.2 - June 4, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New \\"Move Custom Post Types\\" feature that allows you to move your posts into another post type or blog. You can access this feature via Reframe &gt; Advanced.</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fix for single custom post type pages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><strong>Version 1.3.1 - June 2, 2013</strong></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>CSS Transition effect for custom post type page (can be disabled via Reframe &gt; Main Layout &gt; Disable CSS Transition Effects)</li>\r\n<li>Custom post type category filters display items without refreshing the page (Isotope plugin filter)</li>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes for custom post type pages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.3 - May 31, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Galleries for Custom Post Types (<a href="https://northeme.com/wp-admin/\\" target="\\">click here to see details</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Galleries for Gallery Post Formats. Gallery post formats can be shown as slider or gallery (Blog)</li>\r\n<li>Galleries can be used with shortcodes</li>\r\n<li>New pagination feature can be set via Reframe &gt; Main Layout &gt; Pagination. Infinite scroll function is used by default. New \\"Load More\\" option allows you to show more posts by clicking Load More button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.2.1 - May 11, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Intro slider stretching image issue is fixed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.2 - May 10, 2013</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Theme Framework fix : options reset and custom post types issues. All fields are required on Step 2 and Step 3 for custom post types in order to prevent confliction. If you leave a field blank, your custom post type will NOT be saved!</li>\r\n<li>New social icons : behance, sound cloud, amazon, blogger, skype</li>\r\n<li>Fixed : Link issue for images in Composition section</li>\r\n<li>Fixed : Embed video issue for single blog post</li>\r\n<li>Fixed : Text color for Reframe &gt; Styling Options. Text color variable has been changed, you may need to re-select your color preset or re-set your Text color.</li>\r\n<li>Javascript and styling issues were fixed for WP galleries and Jetpack</li>\r\n<li>Additional top paddings are removed to fix left menu and content alignments (h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.1 - May 2, 2013&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Blog overview page fix ; show full content for standard post format</li>\r\n<li>Navigation arrows for Blog</li>\r\n<li>Display categories option for Custom Post Types and Blog</li>\r\n<li>New option :&nbsp;Reframe &gt; Blog Layout &gt; Display Categories</li>\r\n<li>New option :&nbsp;Reframe &gt; Custom Posts - Display Categories option can be set for each post type</li>\r\n<li>New option : Reframe &gt; Blog Layout &gt;&nbsp;Blog info alignment in List View</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.o.4 - April 30, 2013&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Single blog post fix for gallery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.o.3 - April 30, 2013&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Full page slider scrollbar issue has been fixed</li>\r\n<li>New option added : Reframe &gt; Header Settings &gt; Show Submenu Always</li>\r\n<li>Images/Videos panel has been fixed for landscape/portrait options and external URL.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.o.1 - April 22, 2013&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Minor bug fixes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Version 1.o - April 21, 2013&nbsp;</strong></p>\n											]]>\n										</changelog>\n									</notifier>', 'yes'),
